["decision","E6-SKIL1-T2",1776117227,"34dafe5f-6881-4bca-b209-c98c906e3550",{"topic":"How to identify skills that need a binary/scripts","choice":"Source scripts/ directory convention — if skills/\u003cname\u003e/scripts/ exists in source, copy its contents to harness skills/\u003cname\u003e/scripts/","rationale":"Filesystem-driven, no meta.yaml changes needed. New skills declare their script needs by simply creating a scripts/ subdir. The trls skill currently has no scripts/ in source (binary comes from bin/); we will create skills/trls/scripts/ containing a symlink or placeholder that triggers the copy."}]
